slowestQuery.query: SELECT "public"."Subscription"."id", "public"."Subscription"."endpoint", "public"."Subscription"."auth", "public"."Subscription"."p256dh" FROM "public"."Subscription" WHERE ("public"."Subscription"."role" = $1 AND "public"."Subscription"."orderId" = $2 AND "public"."Subscription"."invalidatedAt" IS NULL) OFFSET $3
